    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1896-08-19T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1896-08-19T00:00:00-05:00" n="627"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d627">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Lee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Rockhill</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-08-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 19, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Charles Govin landed from the <hi rend="italic">Three Friends</hi> July 6; joined
                    insurgents; captured in a skirmish on the 9th with Arturo Adrian and Adolfo
                    Mijares. They were bound and taken off. Nothing heard of them since. They are
                    not in the fort nor prisoners.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lee.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
